text: Hi-Octane Coffee is the second album by American singer-songwriter Lili Añel released in 2001 on Original JB Music. Moore —piano on “If” *John Ward —percussion on “If” ;Engineers * Rick Kerr * Julio Peña on “No Matter What Love” * Mastered by Danny Wyatt at Temple of Soul, NYC ==References== Category:2001 albums Category:Lili Añel albums
